15 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that this exemplary care home be
16 appropriately honored during this special time.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
18 the members of this body recognize and commend Hickory Log upon the grand occasion of
19 its 55th anniversary for its decades of service on behalf of those in need as well as extend
20 best wishes for continued success.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
22 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to
23 Hickory Log.
